  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4d54e6da169902b4db8e974e80a3fe1a, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day 3 Radio Transmission
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  mandatory: 0
  lines:
  - AN UPDATE ON THE VIRUS
  - We have been able to confirm a third symptom of the virus.
  - Infected individuals experience discolouration of the chest alongside previously
    disclosed symptoms.
  - However, if the discolouration of the chest is seen at the same time as acne
    on the back, then neither of these symptoms are to be considered when determining
    if an individual is infected.
  - Please continue to be monitor yourself and those around you, and contact us regarding
    anyone you believe to be infected.
